The controller is built on the TI TM4C123 Launch Pad Evaluation Board combined with the GPIO Breakout Booster Pack
- https://www.ti.com/tool/EK-TM4C123GXL
- BOOSTXL-IOBKOUT
Ethernet interface is a Wiznet W5500 - make sure you get a proper one. I had lots of issues with a clone.

all of this can be sources easily from DigiKey or Mouser

Alternatively, use the TI TM4C1294XL board - this one includes the ethernet interface. Some code adaptations will be required.
